These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, ambient
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | airplane |
| Music-Genre       | jazz | ambient |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, chaman
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Cigar   | swisher | chaman |
| Hobby      | sudoku     | writing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, police-officer
1. the designer is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the designer is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Pet   | goat | guinea-pig  |
| Job   | designer | police-officer |

 #################################

 
